ANTHRAX, HUMAN - UNITED KINGDOM (03): (SCOTLAND)
***********************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>

Date: 16 Mar 2010
Source: Health Protection Scotland [edited]
<http://www.hps.scot.nhs.uk/anthrax/index.aspx>


This site provides the latest information on the anthrax cases in
drug users in Scotland and supporting materials developed for those
involved in the outbreak management and the treatment and care of
cases. A number of cases have also been identified in England -- see
<http://www.hpa.org.uk> for information on these cases.

